<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maintenance Mode - Fiona Bot</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f4f6f9;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .maintenance-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .gear-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            animation: spin 4s linear infinite;
        }
        .gear-small {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #4e54c8;
            position: absolute;
            top: 60px;
            right: 140px;
            animation: spin-reverse 3s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        @keyframes spin { 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
        @keyframes spin-reverse { 100% { transform: rotate(-360deg); } }
        
        .bg-pattern {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#4e54c8 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            opacity: 0.05;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="maintenance-card animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <div class="bg-pattern"></div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="position-relative d-inline-block">
                <i class="fas fa-cog gear-icon"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-cog gear-small"></i>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Under Maintenance</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                Sistem atau Sesi Bot sedang dalam perbaikan berkala untuk meningkatkan performa. Silahkan kembali beberapa saat lagi.
            </p>
            
            <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill py-2 fw-bold shadow-sm">
                    <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt me-2"></i> Coba Login (Admin Only)
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/6289526346592" class="btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill py-2 fw-bold">
                    <i class="fas fa-headset me-2"></i> Hubungi Support
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
